{"tid":2457194,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本良心公司推出「傷心假」 偶像結婚可獲10日有薪假","createTime":"2021-03-22T12:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T13:03:32.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e4cb7c354c84c9b2cc22e58ccd1b46d9e3db90","tid":2457194,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:30:40.000Z","msg":"大家覺得一間「好福利」嘅公司有咩條件，係有14個月糧、18日AL、定係有各式各樣嘅醫療福利？最近日本有一間公司，因為有「另類員工福利」而引起熱議，除咗偶像結婚可以請10日有薪「傷心假」，更資助員工睇偶像演唱會。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ev7WhFSUYAMY76R?format=png&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEv7WhFSUYAMY76R%3Fformat%3Dpng%26name%3Dsmall&h=13914fea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣告及MV製作公司Hiroro社長鶴見至善本身就係一位追星族，就連公司名都用日本女團9nine成員村田寬奈嘅暱稱命名。可能因為深諳此道，佢最近推出新員工福利，只要員工頭號偶像宣布結婚或畢業，就可享有10日有薪「傷心假」，而且仲可以視乎傷心程度延長。就算第二或第三鍾意嘅偶像畢業，都可享有3日有薪假期。另外，如果員工要參加頭號偶像演唱會，除咗可以申請早退或請假，更會資助5000日圓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/data/attachment/object_pic/2021/3/22/3c7840ba8eb4de55209edbaf4bf8e061.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fobject_pic%2F2021%2F3%2F22%2F3c7840ba8eb4de55209edbaf4bf8e061.jpg&h=dd425581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到社長鶴見至善Twitter封面嘅相，就知道佢都係一位追星族。（圖片截至：twitter@itaru9Z）<br />\n<br />\n社長鶴見至善表示，上年佢同一位廣告人合作，對方係聲優水樹奈奈嘅粉絲，從東京大學畢業嘅佢，一直以嚟都係一個聰明又隨和嘅人。不過就喺水樹奈奈宣布要結婚嗰一日，對方非常沮喪根本無辦法開會，所以佢先有「傷心假」呢個諗法。不過都唔使咁羨慕住，社長鶴見至善表示現時公司只有三個員工，「傷心假」消息傳出後，就收到超過10份求職信，但現時並無打算請人，見到大家咁支持佢嘅做法覺得非常開心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nlab.itmedia.co.jp/nl/articles/2103/14/news021_2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnlab.itmedia.co.jp%2Fnl%2Farticles%2F2103%2F14%2Fnews021_2.html&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=8a7459ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nlab.itmedia.co.jp/nl/articles/2103/14/news021_2.html</a>"},{"pid":"12003bcff6a82cc05d72149752425dc0a7af7f14","tid":2457194,"uid":224479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:32:04.000Z","msg":"紋身佬同彩啪啪啪<br />\n樓豬要放幾多傷心假"},{"pid":"fabe725e4467fd5ea5543d8a2b9d08e13382c147","tid":2457194,"uid":151926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:32:08.000Z","msg":"所有日本明星都係我偶像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2f85848762227bd0fd506a03909f6bb030ca30","tid":2457194,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:34:04.000Z","msg":"我個名佢今年生埋日都34歲<br />\n適婚年齡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1089c608eb6bd285594eeb9b362116e139905971","tid":2457194,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:38:18.000Z","msg":"KPOP偶像拍拖<br />\n<br />\n粉絲都應該有傷心假🥲"},{"pid":"b26fb9ab1dce6d0f2ab9b397cd54a707dd7e7338","tid":2457194,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12003bcff6a82cc05d72149752425dc0a7af7f14","tid":2457194,"uid":224479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:32:04.000Z","msg":"紋身佬同彩啪啪啪<br />\n樓豬要放幾多傷心假"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:40:43.000Z","msg":"me trust her<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc0a30397a9fcbdb5e041802038ef494fe26d0a","tid":2457194,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1089c608eb6bd285594eeb9b362116e139905971","tid":2457194,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:38:18.000Z","msg":"KPOP偶像拍拖<br />\n<br />\n粉絲都應該有傷心假🥲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:40:54.000Z","msg":"YES<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6842df7fa77843f114bbae1c0e28a1ff437d02e","tid":2457194,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fabe725e4467fd5ea5543d8a2b9d08e13382c147","tid":2457194,"uid":151926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:32:08.000Z","msg":"所有日本明星都係我偶像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"mina sana momo <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74de98debe2a9132e902ba87634f6a42c1aa08d5","tid":2457194,"uid":313222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"解散有冇得放假<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}